[
    {
        "content": "<p>Rietumu pusē sākta būvniecība (nezinu par austrumu), buldozeri rok zemi un ir stabi, kas iezīmē, kur būs ceļš. Un ir atzīmēti koki, kas tiks nocirsti.<br>\nVai būtu jāpārmaina tagi no proposed uz under construction?</p>",
        "id": 489182925,
        "sender_full_name": "Rūdolfs",
        "timestamp": 1734340297
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Pie Rimi un Jelgavas šosejas? Ir bildes?</p>",
        "id": 489183090,
        "sender_full_name": "UrSuS",
        "timestamp": 1734340348
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Atsutīšu bildes ap 15.00</p>",
        "id": 489191079,
        "sender_full_name": "Rūdolfs",
        "timestamp": 1734342610
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Jā pie Rimi un Ozolciema ielas apļa</p>",
        "id": 489191144,
        "sender_full_name": "Rūdolfs",
        "timestamp": 1734342632
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Visticamāk, ka var likt construction, jā. Principā daudzi liek tikko tur pirmais traktors atbrauc.</p>",
        "id": 489206171,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1734347040
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Daudzi liek pirms traktoriem <span aria-label=\"grinning face with smiling eyes\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f601\" role=\"img\" title=\"grinning face with smiling eyes\">:grinning_face_with_smiling_eyes:</span></p>",
        "id": 489207234,
        "sender_full_name": "UrSuS",
        "timestamp": 1734347305
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/D0XS3qbYPtIuW42XY20iNtrK/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.24.jpeg\">WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.24.jpeg</a> Turpinas līdz krustojumam, kur būs domāts aplis <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/84X-29ZYwwnw4MDt3DhdvxuU/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.31.jpeg\">WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.31.jpeg</a> Vienības gatve pielikti stabiņi<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/ToFkIiwY1OJlw-N2Az4jBSKZ/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.33.jpeg\">WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.33.jpeg</a> stabiņi gāja apkārt gar Vienības, Ozolciema un rimi<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/_w0eyw2XdoFKYqevBbeyQimp/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.36.jpeg\">WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.36.jpeg</a> Rimi un pietura <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/_gUoqdU4M88DwF2vllb6AcuJ/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.39.jpeg\">WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.39.jpeg</a> Rimi un pietura<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/_kXz4bDLMPfAEmQQMRKJ88qU/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.40.jpeg\">WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.40.jpeg</a> Pie apļa<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/irQTcln9_rMbqD9HqdfVvCr9/WhatsApp-Image-2024-nat-14.28.40.jpeg\">WhatsApp Image 2024-nat 14.28.40.jpeg</a> Pie apļa</p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/D0XS3qbYPtIuW42XY20iNtrK/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.24.jpeg\" title=\"WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.24.jpeg\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"4080x3060\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/D0XS3qbYPtIuW42XY20iNtrK/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.24.jpeg/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/84X-29ZYwwnw4MDt3DhdvxuU/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.31.jpeg\" title=\"WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.31.jpeg\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"4080x3060\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/84X-29ZYwwnw4MDt3DhdvxuU/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.31.jpeg/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/ToFkIiwY1OJlw-N2Az4jBSKZ/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.33.jpeg\" title=\"WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.33.jpeg\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"4080x3060\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/ToFkIiwY1OJlw-N2Az4jBSKZ/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.33.jpeg/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/_w0eyw2XdoFKYqevBbeyQimp/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.36.jpeg\" title=\"WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.36.jpeg\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"4080x3060\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/_w0eyw2XdoFKYqevBbeyQimp/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.36.jpeg/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/_gUoqdU4M88DwF2vllb6AcuJ/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.39.jpeg\" title=\"WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.39.jpeg\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"4080x3060\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/_gUoqdU4M88DwF2vllb6AcuJ/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.39.jpeg/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/_kXz4bDLMPfAEmQQMRKJ88qU/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.40.jpeg\" title=\"WhatsApp Image 2024-12-16 at 14.28.40.jpeg\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"4080x3060\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/_kXz4bDLMPfAEmQQMRKJ88qU/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-14.28.40.jpeg/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/irQTcln9_rMbqD9HqdfVvCr9/WhatsApp-Image-2024-nat-14.28.40.jpeg\" title=\"WhatsApp Image 2024-nat 14.28.40.jpeg\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"4080x3060\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/irQTcln9_rMbqD9HqdfVvCr9/WhatsApp-Image-2024-nat-14.28.40.jpeg/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
