    {
        "content": "<p>Paldies! <span aria-label=\"+1\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44d\" role=\"img\" title=\"+1\">:+1:</span></p>",
        "id": 489232384,
        "sender_full_name": "UrSuS",
        "timestamp": 1734354616
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Tag%3Abarrier%3Dstabins\">barrier=stabins</a></p>",
        "id": 489240016,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1734356567
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Tag:barrier%3Dbollard\">barrier=bollard</a>?</p>",
        "id": 489247091,
        "sender_full_name": "Rūdolfs",
        "timestamp": 1734358291
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ja nopietni, tad tos nekartē, jo tie ir temporary. Apkārt var uzzīmēt contruction landuse</p>",
        "id": 489247875,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1734358453
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Nu jā tā domāju, bet ja iezīmē construction, tad nav jāliek arī kopā ar brownfield?</p>",
        "id": 489248179,
        "sender_full_name": "Rūdolfs",
        "timestamp": 1734358537
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Es domāju, kad būs jau uzrakuši zemi, bet neko vēl \"uzbūvējuši\" vai \"būvē\"</p>",
        "id": 489248898,
        "sender_full_name": "Rūdolfs",
        "timestamp": 1734358715
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Kopā diez vai, brownfield tas ir \"nekas nenotiek\" un parasti pamests. Ja ir reāls plāns un darbi bīdās visam projektam kopā, tad tas būs labāk jau construction.</p>",
        "id": 489249759,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1734358926
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Vienības gatvē, kur sadalas ceļš uz 2, ir aizslēgta labā braukšanas puse, un ir pārvietots uz otra ceļa pusi, kas aizņem tikai vienu joslu. Vajadzētu iezīmēt, pievienoju note, kur apmēram ir pievienots ceļš, pa kuru ir jāpārvietojas uz otru pusi.</p>",
        "id": 490104777,
        "sender_full_name": "Rūdolfs",
        "timestamp": 1734678281
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/note/4557643\">Note</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/note/4557643\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a2f2f7777772e6f70656e7374726565746d61702e6f72672f6173736574732f6f736d5f6c6f676f5f3235362d656430323866393034363832323461323732393631633338306563656530636662373362383034386233346634623462323034623766306431303937383735642e706e67&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/note/4557643\" title=\"Note: 4557643\">Note: 4557643</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">OpenStreetMap is a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license.</div></div></div>",
        "id": 490105620,
        "sender_full_name": "Rūdolfs",
        "timestamp": 1734678799
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Man ir shēma, atjaunošu</p>",
        "id": 490106638,
        "sender_full_name": "UrSuS",
        "timestamp": 1734679317
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Pats galvenais, ka Mapillary vismaz vienreiz pa vecajām vietām izbraukts, lai iemūžinātu. Tas laikam ir lielākais projekts, ko es zinu, kur tik daudz pilnībā pārbūvē bet ir safilmēts vecais. Austrumu maģistrāle laikam tuvākais, bet tur arī izmantotas pārsvarā esošās ielas. Pat Ķekavas apvedceļš bija pārsvarā pa jaunu trajektoriju un tur Mapillary tikai pa šķērsielām/stigām pārbraucot pāri. A te gandrīz 3 kilometri pa pārsvarā esošiem ceļiem un ielām.</p>",
        "id": 490160979,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1734701309
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Apbraucu pa jau uzbūvēto <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=19/56.902857/24.133389\">Dienvidu tiltu</a> (austrumu daļa 4. kārtai), ir arī iesākti būvarbi.</p>\n<p>Bet ir jautājums, kā būtu jāiezīmē (<a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/1344562225\">šeit</a>), kur ir \"celtnieku mājas\", parasti konteineri un pagaidu ceļi? Pagaidām esmu to iezīmējis kā construction area.<br>\nTad vēl ir pārmainītas joslas <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/note/4558802\">šeit</a>, no divām uz vienu, nēesmu vēl sapratis kādēļ (divas joslas ir joprojām uz ziemeļiem, bet no tā note ir tikai viena, līdz Ziepniekkalna ielai).</p>\n<p>Par citu vēl nezinu, vajadzētu apskatīties.</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=19/56.902857/24.133389\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a2f2f7777772e6f70656e7374726565746d61702e6f72672f6173736574732f6f736d5f6c6f676f5f3235362d656430323866393034363832323461323732393631633338306563656530636662373362383034386233346634623462323034623766306431303937383735642e706e67&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=19/56.902857/24.133389\" title=\"OpenStreetMap\">OpenStreetMap</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">OpenStreetMap is a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license.</div></div></div><div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/1344562225\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a2f2f7777772e6f70656e7374726565746d61702e6f72672f6173736574732f6f736d5f6c6f676f5f3235362d656430323866393034363832323461323732393631633338306563656530636662373362383034386233346634623462323034623766306431303937383735642e706e67&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/1344562225\" title=\"Way: 1344562225\">Way: 1344562225</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">OpenStreetMap is a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license.</div></div></div><div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/note/4558802\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a2f2f7777772e6f70656e7374726565746d61702e6f72672f6173736574732f6f736d5f6c6f676f5f3235362d656430323866393034363832323461323732393631633338306563656530636662373362383034386233346634623462323034623766306431303937383735642e706e67&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/note/4558802\" title=\"Note: 4558802\">Note: 4558802</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">OpenStreetMap is a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license.</div></div></div>",
        "id": 490311222,
        "sender_full_name": "Rūdolfs",
        "timestamp": 1734798171
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Es neko vairāk par construction neliktu būvdarbu teritorijām (pagaidu ceļiem, konteineriem, mājiņām, tehnikas novietnēm, utt.) - tas viss temporary un jēgas īsti nav no tādiem datiem salīdzinot ar ieguldīto laiku.</p>",
        "id": 490311384,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1734798360
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Te tas it kā 3 gadus viss, tāpēc iezīmēt construction vajadzētu un vietas, kur nevar nokļūt, visus ceļus un takas novākt vai access salikt. Bet vairāk par to grūti spriest</p>",
        "id": 490311465,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1734798423
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ja tu esi gatavs regulāri tādas lietas kā joslu skaitu skatīties... nu var jau protams. Bet tas baigais darbs sekot, kas kur notiek. Visu laiku mainās un mainīsies. Kamēr kaut kādi navigatori dabūs to datus, tie jau būs atkal veci...</p>",
        "id": 490311498,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1734798471
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Par to vienu joslu laikam tāpēc, lai laicīgi sabremzētu satiksmi pirms savienojas ar ceļu, kur būs sānos pārbūve un arī viena josla. Bet nu to es galīgi minu.</p>",
        "id": 490311679,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1734798631
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It kā ir jau plānojumā sazīmēti visas taku <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/1324175456\">pāriešanas vietas</a> un vēl citur, piekrītu par joslām.</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/1324175456\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a2f2f7777772e6f70656e7374726565746d61702e6f72672f6173736574732f6f736d5f6c6f676f5f3235362d656430323866393034363832323461323732393631633338306563656530636662373362383034386233346634623462323034623766306431303937383735642e706e67&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/1324175456\" title=\"Way: 1324175456\">Way: 1324175456</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">OpenStreetMap is a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license.</div></div></div>",
        "id": 490311996,
        "sender_full_name": "Rūdolfs",
        "timestamp": 1734798922
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Tag%3Afootway%3Dpath\">footway=path</a> <span aria-label=\"upside down\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f643\" role=\"img\" title=\"upside down\">:upside_down:</span> --&gt; <a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Tag%3Ahighway%3Dproposed\">highway=proposed</a> + <a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Tag%3Aproposed%3Dfootway\">proposed=footway</a> (vai <a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Tag%3Aproposed%3Ahighway%3Dfootway\">proposed:highway=footway</a>)</p>",
        "id": 490312936,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1734799823
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Interesants tunelis iekšā mežā... velo/gājēj infrastruktūra kā parasti izskatās</p>",
        "id": 490312973,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1734799885
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Jā, iedzīvotājiem ir ļoti iecienīts mežs, kur pastaigāties un izbaudīt dabu, nepietiek ar Ēbeļmuižas parku.</p>",
        "id": 490313709,
        "sender_full_name": "Rūdolfs",
        "timestamp": 1734800556
    }
]